{"tid":2396302,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人煮Carbonara煮到有臭汗味？？？","createTime":"2021-02-05T13:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T13:50:43.000Z","uid":340502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b058b1a243f3b0b71735d1120d9d0757857557b","tid":2396302,"uid":340502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:02:07.000Z","msg":"事源係咁<br />\n小弟今日煮carbonara<br />\n當我炒煙肉個時<br />\n炒極都唔濃<br />\n我已經覺得好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁煮完試味我都覺得冇問題<br />\n（利申我嗅覺同味覺都有問題<br />\n咁諗住比屋企人試下我啲手勢咁啦<br />\n之後我家姐問我：<br />\n喂！你係咪做完運動冇沖涼<br />\n我話：<br />\n沖左架啦喎，第2件衫黎<br />\n之後佢就話你地有冇人覺得唔知邊到有臭汗味<br />\n但最後discuss完都係覺得來源不明<br />\n咁開飯我問家姐：<br />\n你覺得啲carbonara 點<br />\n咁佢就靜音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢地問老豆：<br />\n你覺得有冇臭汗味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老豆係廚師黎<br />\n佢就話：<br />\n啲煙肉<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n臭架喎！<br />\n佢地就好似如夢初醒咁話：<br />\n係喎，啲臭汗味真係啲煙肉到爆出黎<br />\n到底係咩煙肉會整到有臭汗味？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n.<br />\n（利申我自我感覺良好，唔覺得係我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966ee915b11e75ad0329dd289ba1d45c69e613b8","tid":2396302,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"你用煙肉定guanciale<br />\n如果煙肉就係壞咗<br />\nguanciale嘅話只係你唔習慣佢啲funky notes"},{"pid":"1cec5c9a824fa7068cd9c8987ff4de8f7f6b856f","tid":2396302,"uid":340502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"966ee915b11e75ad0329dd289ba1d45c69e613b8","tid":2396302,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"你用煙肉定guanciale<br />\n如果煙肉就係壞咗<br />\nguanciale嘅話只係你唔習慣佢啲funky notes"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"煙肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56746ab9c476fd708eb97a040c69bd89fec2009d","tid":2396302,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知道自己啲嗅覺同味覺有問題<br />\n咁試黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042cb2092fc1cdfd77e7eb1eda262fa39401ea33","tid":2396302,"uid":340502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56746ab9c476fd708eb97a040c69bd89fec2009d","tid":2396302,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知道自己啲嗅覺同味覺有問題<br />\n咁試黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"見啲人煮飯仔都會試味，咁咪試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}